{"tid":1492592,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得個社會開始回復平靜? :)","createTime":"2019-08-21T01:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T02:52:54.000Z","uid":287028,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a0905f75e9e6aa4de415701af7adaba2427b06e2","tid":1492592,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:51:41.000Z","msg":"好多身邊朋友開始覺得唔洗點理啦，<br />\n自然會有人做野;<br />\n連登仔會做野;<br />\n議員會做野;<br />\n其他市民會做野。<br />\n工作，家庭已經長時間被忽略，不如用番多啲時間行街睇戲食飯Happy下啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每多一個人有呢個想法，大家就少一分力量。 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">當100 個人咁諗，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當1000 個人咁諗，</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">當10000 個人咁諗，</span><br />\n仲邊有人企出黎為不平發聲?<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家好攰，但真係要堅持住!<br />\n老套啲講句，<br />\n我地最大敵人係自己<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">決心</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">意志</span></span>!<br />\n當你開始覺得不如就咁算啦，<br />\n我地仲係輸緊0:5呀!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求一樣都冇!<br />\n6條人命!<br />\n700個市民被捕!<br />\n最少50名義士被私刑暴打!性羞辱!</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人地為你付出青春，付出肉身，唔通你連少少時間同金錢都要吝嗇?</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都好似你地一樣咁攰，都要返工照顧屋企人。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應承我，一齊堅持到10月1號得唔得?</span></strong><br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n一個都不能少"},{"pid":"5fcfb76774a0c56383ea684899643a8e3fd8d34a","tid":1492592,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:52:07.000Z","msg":"香港人"},{"pid":"9faebebbf26137462b8ea4bea722c981db318777","tid":1492592,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:52:17.000Z","msg":"堅持"},{"pid":"d5c6dffc5783ad3c240c3f26c6a1e7157af1309e","tid":1492592,"uid":287028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"香港人"},{"pid":"00774